- Singleton is a design pattern that restricts a class to a single instance. Example:

      ```dart
      class Singleton {
        Singleton._privateConstructor();

        static final Singleton _instance = Singleton._privateConstructor();

        factory Singleton() {
          return _instance;
        }
      }
      ```

